<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.4.3">
<l>ilaṅkaiyuṅ kaṭalu maṭalarun tuppi</l>
<l>ṉirunitik kiṟaivaṉu marakkar</l>
<l>kulaṅkaḷuṅ keṭamuṉ koṭuntoḻil purinta</l>
<l>koṟṟavaṉ koḻuñcuṭar cuḻaṉṟa</l>
<l>vilaṅkali luriñci mēlniṉṟa vicumpil</l>
<l>veṇtukil koṭiyeṉa virintu</l>
<l>valantaru maṇinīrk kaṅkaiyiṉ karaimēl</l>
<l>vatariyāc ciramat tuḷḷāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The victor who once took fierce action to destroy the demon race,</l>
<l>Lanka, the sea, and the king of two treasures of valor difficult to conquer,</l>
<l>He is the one in Badarī Āśrama on the banks of the Ganges</l>
<l rend="indent">whose crystal waters generate strength,</l>
<l>Unfurling like a white cloth flag [and] anointing the mountain</l>
<l rend="indent">where circles the full sun in the sky that stands above.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
